## Quality gate

```bash
uvx pre-commit run --all-files
```

The gate runs the repository's `pre-commit` hooks: universal hygiene (whitespace, EOF, YAML/TOML
validity, merge-conflict markers, large-file and secret scanning) plus the governance checks
(Actions SHA-pinning, verbatim licence, root-Markdown allowlist, and `docs/` frontmatter). A
language stack overlay adds its own lint, type-check, and test steps on top.

## Governance

This repository follows the `repo-structure-standard`, `repo-hygiene`, and `governance-standards`
conventions; see `AGENTS.md` for the agent-facing contract.

